
Kinect Tracking with OSC
openframeworks app using ofxOpenNI to track a user, overal visuals over the hands and communicate via OSC.

Becky Stewart
April 2012


Requirements:

ofxOpenNI
ofxOsc
ofxXmlSettings


XML file osc_settings.xml holds the IP address and port information for OSC server and client.  File needs to in ./bin/data relative to project.
